{"tid":845638,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中新社專訪梁振英：人生價值非銀行存款，而是為國家付出","createTime":"2018-10-02T23:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T16:15:13.000Z","uid":195944,"like":61,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e6cc95128c2fa9a94894b6db6a1cb541c0fa15d1","tid":845638,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:32:18.000Z","msg":"今年是內地改革開放40周年，中新社就此題目專訪全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英。梁振英表示，40年來，香港在國家各領域改革開放中得益甚多，香港年輕人如今有更多機會，惟強調「<span style=\"color: red;\">凡事不能僅用商業角度看國家與香港的關係</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在專訪中向記者展示多張舊照，包括深圳發展之初他北上視察及講課照片。他說，香港在國家各領域改革開放中得益甚多，並以40年來內地GDP實質增長了34倍，香港人均GDP以美元計增長了11倍數據作例，直言「香港為國家的改革開放一直作出重要貢獻，而國家的發展亦成就了今天的香港&mdash;&mdash;香港和內地實現合作共贏，香港也是『受益者』」。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英又稱，隨着國際形勢不斷變化，香港社會應提振年輕人報效國家的奉獻精神：「<span style=\"color: red;\">人生最有價值的地方並非銀行有多少存款，而是能為國家付出多少。</span>今天香港的年輕人，機會更多，但凡事不能僅用商業角度看國家與香港的關係，在要求國家給予『國民待遇』的同時，也應該承擔國民責任。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181002/s00001/1538468611770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181002%2Fs00001%2F1538468611770&d=iUr0gEzqSs0uuOOQL8Ar1LDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=743d2e71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181002%2Fs00001%2F1538468611770&h=14ecd3ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181002/s00001/1538468611770</a><br />\n<br />\n特首就應如此愛蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩理由人工仲高過蟈家主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該象徵收1蚊 以報答蟈家恩寵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家說對不對？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47086ceeeafa4eea0846f70bd368034733b40c29","tid":845638,"uid":195944,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:33:34.000Z","msg":"四十幾萬一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪唔愛蟈？ <br />\n<br />\n係咪想搞港獨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc65f0f6213f79fc63bcfb21416baea2c67294a8","tid":845638,"uid":71748,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:35:42.000Z","msg":"國家收返佢五千萬先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096a12bf4d8d19ad531cbf915f0c2602646797b1","tid":845638,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:47:03.000Z","msg":"所以不嬲都叫壓支那人食草"},{"pid":"7e0089696985e65927f519dba8045adc423bb652","tid":845638,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:48:12.000Z","msg":"咁識擦鞋"},{"pid":"2baa8b21e88d1a1881d01ce2db6b860f2c13889a","tid":845638,"uid":1723,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:51:08.000Z","msg":"咁就得啦<br />\n拎晒你啲錢開大鑊飯<br />\n拎你赤柱間屋整人民公社同啲年輕人住啦"},{"pid":"0202383c9588122fb43501499aaf3f5ae1b73371","tid":845638,"uid":52595,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:55:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9503c6471afdca6acc84f88e439a13306da536df","tid":845638,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:01:11.000Z","msg":"咁愛蟈，去美國代肥平受啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e98e151efbc49e89c89d41cd9922f8eeba56ae","tid":845638,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re